{"tid":1327153,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國男團開con竟然開到沙烏地阿拉伯","createTime":"2019-07-17T13:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T14:54:20.000Z","uid":221236,"like":6,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dcb6f59e95baf682d02f91abba996a8a9a1885eb","tid":1327153,"uid":221236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:07:55.000Z","msg":"近日，南韓流行音樂團體「防彈少年團」(BTS)宣布將在今年十月到沙烏地阿拉伯開唱，引起了正反兩面的討論，外界也在觀察沙國如何透過廣邀國際大咖歌手發展娛樂產業。現在，最受國際樂壇關注、即將到沙國開唱的音樂團體就是南韓「防彈少年團」(BTS)，他們早已走出亞洲、席捲歐美樂壇，在中東也擁有大量粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n按照目前的計畫，BTS將在今年 10月11日在首都利雅德(Riyadh)的法赫德國王國際體育場(King Fahd International Stadium)開唱，這裡總共可以容納超過 6萬8,000名觀眾。屆時，他們將成為第一個在沙國體育場舉行單獨非拼盤式演唱會的歌手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6WnonDT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6WnonDT.png&h=90bdc4f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e2e0aa9883a6bc5ac143edf3150c9dbc08c8c71","tid":1327153,"uid":221236,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:12:15.000Z","msg":"未滿十八歲單身女性不能踏進阿拉伯<br />\n咁啲女fans點去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7427a348fa85ed1123d55e3670102876ed653de6","tid":1327153,"uid":43493,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:25:21.000Z","msg":"好多酋長鍾意屌屎眼<br />\n擺明去賣菊花啦"},{"pid":"d34d618438135dcea18fc965e594d276487299c6","tid":1327153,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:27:03.000Z","msg":"空難啦"},{"pid":"ad1636b251e96ddbe9e100fde798cd7dfbf7e7a6","tid":1327153,"uid":221132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7427a348fa85ed1123d55e3670102876ed653de6","tid":1327153,"uid":43493,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:25:21.000Z","msg":"好多酋長鍾意屌屎眼<br />\n擺明去賣菊花啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:30:33.000Z","msg":"酋長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tong